"In this section, we explore the nature of the correlations
between mass accretion rate and the large-scale halo environ-
ment (characterised by halo bias b1; see section 2.5) in fixed
mass bins, also known as halo assembly bias or secondary
bias."
Previous studies have largely focused on secondary halo
